  "title": "Admin Assistant #81476",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: F&B Vending Service</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Admin Assistant</strong></li><li>Working Location: Bukit Merah (Walk distance from MRT)</li><li>Working Hours: Monday – Friday (8.45am – 5.30pm), Alternate Saturday (8.45am – 12.45pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary (Yearly increment) + Variable Bonus (Profit Sharing)</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Respond to general and administrative emails and attend to sales, customer, and general enquiries.</li><li>Handle customer hotline feedback/ complaints, follow up where necessary, and maintain accurate customer contract files and records.</li><li>Maintain proper record of sales and petty cash.</li><li>Prepare and consolidate monthly reports and required documents for drivers.</li><li>Perform cash-handling and related duties, including counting notes and coins.</li><li>Update servicing/ maintenance logs based on information provided by the Operations Manager and Technician.</li><li>Conduct weekly check of company vehicle GPS systems and basic inspections.</li><li>Support other administrative tasks as assigned.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum GCE ‘O’ Level.</li><li>At least 1 year of related administrative experience.</li><li>Strong interpersonal, customer service, and communication abilities.</li><li>Basic skills in Microsoft Excel reporting.</li><li>Well-organised, and comfortable working in a fast-paced environment.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#81476 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
